OL,6,FThese include how land and property no
OL,7,Flonger needed will be disposed of,
OL,8,Fimpacts on other rail projects
OL,9,Fdependent on the cancelled phases,
OL,10,Fwhat will be delivered with the money
OL,11,Fsaved, and how HS2 trains will operate
OL,12,Fon existing lines.
